{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Overview</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Abject Abyss is a first person horror adventure. Take the roll of Ernest Sheffield, a technician, and one of many staff employed by the enormous Luminary Corporation on the distant world of Marzanna. It's been steady work for two years, but everything is about to fall apart.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Explore</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3353810/extras/Reactor.gif?t=1739759213\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore your surroundings to find useful items. Stims and medications to heal wounds, lost security key fobs, clipboards with vital information, and more scattered across the dark corners of the facility.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Evade</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3353810/extras/Monster.gif?t=1739759213\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are many dangers inside the collapsing facility, and Ernest isn\u2019t a soldier. Evade danger with care and cunning, and when that fails? Run.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Solve Puzzles</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3353810/extras/Puzzle.gif?t=1739759213\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">From opening a locked door to restarting a nuclear reactor, use your wits and technical skills to progress through the facility, even as everything falls apart around you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Linear hand crafted levels, with room for exploration</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A variety of twisted monsters. Encounter new horrors as you progress</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Simple inventory management. Collect items, but don\u2019t worry about weight or limited space</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A focus on building tension and atmosphere rather than repetitive jumpscares</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Straightforward puzzles that don't require nonsense item combinations or insane logic</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3353810/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739759213","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3353810/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1739759213","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3353810/4df3403c544efcd7e00136bfd6f917fc2505d0d1/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739759213","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3353810/4df3403c544efcd7e00136bfd6f917fc2505d0d1/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739759213","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":"This game contains strong horror themes, Body-horror, gore (such as corpses), and depictions of violence."},"detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Overview</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Abject Abyss is a first person horror adventure. Take the roll of Ernest Sheffield, a technician, and one of many staff employed by the enormous Luminary Corporation on the distant world of Marzanna. It's been steady work for two years, but everything is about to fall apart.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Explore</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3353810/extras/Reactor.gif?t=1739759213\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore your surroundings to find useful items. Stims and medications to heal wounds, lost security key fobs, clipboards with vital information, and more scattered across the dark corners of the facility.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Evade</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3353810/extras/Monster.gif?t=1739759213\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are many dangers inside the collapsing facility, and Ernest isn\u2019t a soldier. Evade danger with care and cunning, and when that fails? Run.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Solve Puzzles</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3353810/extras/Puzzle.gif?t=1739759213\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">From opening a locked door to restarting a nuclear reactor, use your wits and technical skills to progress through the facility, even as everything falls apart around you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Linear hand crafted levels, with room for exploration</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A variety of twisted monsters. Encounter new horrors as you progress</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Simple inventory management. Collect items, but don\u2019t worry about weight or limited space</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A focus on building tension and atmosphere rather than repetitive jumpscares</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Straightforward puzzles that don't require nonsense item combinations or insane logic</p></li></ul>","developers":["Anton Bezett"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3353810/header.jpg?t=1739759213","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul cl